chat_history.content:
Here is a list of the seven largest islands in the world, along with their respective capital cities:

1. Greenland - Nuuk
2. New Guinea - Port Moresby
3. Borneo - Nusantara
4. Madagascar - Antananarivo
5. Baffin Island - There is no official capital city for Baffin Island.
6. Sumatra - Medan
7. Honshu - Tokyo

Note that Baffin Island does not have a designated capital city. It is a large island in the Canadian Arctic Archipelago and is divided into several territories and provinces, each with their own administrative centers.
